Jean Desailly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Desailly 0 Jean Desailly (24 August 1920 – 11 June 2008) was a French actor. He was a member of the Comédie-Française from 1942 to 1946, and later participated in about 90 movies. Jean_Desailly ( 24_August_1920 – 11_June_2008 ) was a_French_actor .
